headline: Franklin Growth Opportunities SMA Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: The fund underperformed the Russell 3000 Growth Index benchmark in the fourth quarter. US economy appears to be firing on all cylinders heading into 2025, with no signs of a major slowdown.
